data.description: Cute home on large lot convenient to shopping and restaurants. Large eat in kitchen. 3rd bedroom is currently used as Living room off kitchen. Large sunroom that is used as a playroom. Upstairs has a bedroom area with a separate space as well! This home has lots of closet space. Detached garage has a space behind that would be great for outdoor entertaining.  Fenced yard & patio area
